WEBVTT


1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.140
Soooo, where did we leave off?

2
00:00:06.109 --> 00:00:09.900
Kesh was the only survivor, and he met the Creator himself.

3
00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:14.660
The Creator told him that three tokens are needed to enter Tokenville.

4
00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:20.400
And he sent Kesh back to the past, where all his friends were still alive.

5
00:00:21.860 --> 00:00:23.480
It all started again.

6
00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:26.790
Kesh saw all his friends and he was very happy.

7
00:00:26.790 --> 00:00:32.040
Wise Nao is standing on a rock again, giving his famous speech.

8
00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:33.120
"STOP!"

9
00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:35.830
His speech is interrupted by a loud voice from afar.

10
00:00:35.830 --> 00:00:37.820
"Who are you?"

11
00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:42.180
The crowd is amazed, as Kesh walks to the stone and asks for the floor.

12
00:00:42.180 --> 00:00:44.470
"I came from the future to warn you!"

13
00:00:44.470 --> 00:00:49.500
"We will be able to find the promised land... only if there are three of us left".

14
00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:53.400
"All the others... they have to... die".

15
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:55.850
"All, except for three?"

16
00:00:55.850 --> 00:00:57.829
- shouts someone from the crowd.

17
00:00:57.829 --> 00:00:59.590
"Yes", - Kesh answers.

18
00:00:59.590 --> 00:01:02.920
"Since we all are destined to die, you will be the first!"

19
00:01:03.080 --> 00:01:03.980
Boom!

20
00:01:04.540 --> 00:01:06.840
And a fierce bloody battle began.

21
00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:10.940
Everyone started to fight using random weapons and even sticks,

22
00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:15.920
and some tokens were throwing stones, although it's very, very bad.

23
00:01:15.930 --> 00:01:19.149
A lot of tokens perished in this horrid fight.

24
00:01:19.149 --> 00:01:23.200
A few heroes survived the bloodbath, but they were exhausted,

25
00:01:23.220 --> 00:01:26.960
so they decided to stop killing each other, and have some rest.

26
00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:33.530
Which heroes are still alive?

27
00:01:33.530 --> 00:01:35.890
You will find it out next time.

28
00:01:35.890 --> 00:01:39.820
And for now, good night, sleep tight.